{
  "stem": "71.4",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She finds time to take children on a trip or do something in the Temple or sell-- sell some scripts.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Whatever there is to do, Estelle is there to do.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You and your husband, you've been extremely active in the Jewish community.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And you've contributed a lot.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, a lot-- a lot to thank God for what we have.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And others did not live to have it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And also, I think they say charity begins at home, but what you see, what your parents are doing, I think you learn that you cannot live for yourself.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You have to help you-- other people, too.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We-- as soon as we came to Los Angeles, we joined the 1939 Club.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We are very active.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We directed a chair, a Holocaust chair, and-- and Dr.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Goetz I'm sure you know, Samuel Goetz.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He was the initiator of that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We have a-- we have a plaque.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Our name is mentioned on the plaque.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'm happy we could help.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I am very happy we could.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You can see we have here-- maybe we can show it later, that is a-- the top letter [INAUDIBLE] on-- on the wall of the-- and we also belong-- I am from Lodz, so I belong to the Lodz organization.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "At our 40th anniversary, we made a party in the Friar's Club, and all-- all the-- instead of gifts, people made donations, and the money was sent to the Tel HaShomer Hospital in Tel Aviv.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was quite-- quite a nice sum of money that was collected that time.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We also support [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Habat. ?] Every year I know they're doing a good job.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Maybe some people are not agreeing with me but we saw it.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
